        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Hanying', 3: '...You\\'re here.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'Today is the Double Seventh Festival. I was thinking about the time I spent in Kowloong, when I often heard stories about reunion and waiting. I put those feelings into the dance you just saw. I wonder if it was to your liking... and whether my dancing has improved?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'It\\'s beautiful.', 3: '19', 4: '(Applaud)', 5: '19'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Hanying clasps her hands in front of her, looking at you as if both confessing and testing your reaction.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'Noise has its moment, but silence has its own rhythm. There\\'s a music performance from Kowloong in central Constellia today. May I invite you to watch it with me?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A trace of sandalwood mixes with the smell of caramel from sugar art stalls in the distance, creating a strange prelude to the Double Seventh Festival.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'As the sound of traditional string and bamboo instruments reaches you, Kowloong\\'s ancient charm seems to wind around your wrists. Your breathing unconsciously grows closer, until in the hazy light of the lanterns, it feels connected.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500916', 3: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'You turn your head to see the cyan-green mechanoid smiling at you.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'So this is... Kowloong\\'s traditional music?', 3: '27'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'Yes. Even in a mechanical body, it\\'s hard not to be moved by such rhythm and beauty. This piece is called \"The Magpie Bridge Immortal\".', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'In Kowloong legend, on this day magpies form a bridge for a fairy to reunite with her long-separated lover under the moonlight.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'The fairy waited a long time, but her lover was kept on the other side of the Milky Way. Even though they meet in dreams, waking brings sadness. That\\'s why this melody carries the meaning of \"no regrets.\"', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '7'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'It\\'s like... ah, I\\'ve been talking so much. You aren\\'t bored, are you, 【kuroname】?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Not at all.', 3: '33', 4: 'I love it.', 5: '33'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Hanying lowers her head slightly, her hair falling to hide her faint blush.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'Commandant, may I invite you to dance with me to \"The Magpie Bridge Immortal\"?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Of course.', 3: '40', 4: 'I\\'m afraid I\\'ll step on your toes...', 5: '37'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Hanying laughs softly and waves a hand.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'I wouldn\\'t make it difficult for you. Just a few simple partner steps, nothing complicated. All that matters is moving in sync.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'Here, give me your hand. Relax and follow my lead.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "DialogDisable",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She extends her hand gracefully, palm up, an invitation impossible to refuse.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '(Extend your hand)', 3: '42'}"
    },
